---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy — Chitti" description="Learn how Chitti protects your privacy and handles your data with care.">

  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-light">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-policy mt-12 space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Our Privacy Promise</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Chitti is built with privacy at its core. We believe your appearance data is deeply personal, and we treat it that way. Here's how we protect you.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Photo Privacy</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Photos are processed in real-time and are <strong class="text-text">never permanently stored</strong> on our servers.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>We use short-lived signed URLs that expire automatically. No raw image data is retained.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>No images appear in server logs or analytics. Only metadata (timestamps, analysis type) is logged.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We collect only what's necessary to provide our service:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Account info:</strong> Phone number (for authentication), display name, region preference.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Conversation history:</strong> Your chat history with AI specialists, stored securely so you can revisit past feedback.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Product data:</strong> Products you add to your collection (name, type, routine slot) to personalize recommendations.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Preferences:</strong> Tone preference, persona selection, context choices — to tailor your experience.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            All data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest. We use Supabase with row-level security, meaning your data is accessible only to you. Our backend never proxies raw image data — only signed URLs with short expiration.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We use the following third-party services to provide Chitti:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Supabase</strong> — Authentication and database (with row-level security).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">OpenAI</strong> — AI analysis and feedback generation. Photos are sent for analysis and are subject to OpenAI's data processing policies.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Account Deletion</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            You can delete your account at any time from the app settings. This permanently removes all your data — profile, conversations, products, and preferences. This action is irreversible.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Questions about privacy? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:privacy@chitti.me" class="font-medium text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">privacy@chitti.me</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
